{"tid":1992674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反修例事件28宗公務員懷疑貪污案　26宗涉及警員","createTime":"2020-04-28T09:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T09:59:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c470abfeaad1e9ff09975bb7b4836387b9472168","tid":1992674,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"廉政公署表示，截至今年2月底，正處理28宗反修例事件中涉及公務員的懷疑貪污個案，其中26宗涉及警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n廉政公署回覆民主黨議員林卓廷，於立法會特別財委會的查詢，指目前28宗於反修例事件中涉及公務員的懷疑貪污個案之中，有26宗涉及警務人員。林卓廷要求廉政公署交代涉及的警員人數。<br />\n<br />\n廉署表示，基於保密原則，廉政公署不適宜透露個案資料，包括涉案警務人員的數目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523223-20200428.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523223-20200428.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=e52e65fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523223-20200428.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c7a143c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523223-20200428.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f74c8e9e7f1893606b5f14341ac12ef9d8be789f","tid":1992674,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:47:40.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134e6fbe152831b6f16b392fa1f77bcfa1e5d7ce","tid":1992674,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"檢控未"},{"pid":"4d9809ca35c25f796e71d2d2dfcb70673d405718","tid":1992674,"uid":66049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"肯定無咁少<br />\n721都唔知收咗幾多"},{"pid":"86f1318737b4c73547674a8eafa7d8c6d43fd4bb","tid":1992674,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:59:15.000Z","ms